{"word":"G1551 - ἐκδέχομαι - ekdéchomai - ek-dekh'-om-ahee - Expect","slug":"G1551","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐκδέχομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ekdéchomai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ek-dekh'-om-ahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Expect"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B5;&#x0313;&#x03BA;&#x03B4;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C7;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B9; - ekdechomai</b> - <i>ek-dekh'-om-ahee</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G1537\">G1537</a> and <a href=\"#/G1209\">G1209</a>; to <i>accept from</i> some source, that is, (by implication) to <i>await:</i> - expect, look (tarry) for, wait (for)."}]}